title: commander keen game *V.3 released in exe*
content:
EDIT 2: Version 3 is now released, to spare you the trouble I will link to it right here:
[url=http://host-a.net/getfile.php?usern=yodablob&file=Commander%20Keenv.3.exe]host-a.net/getfile.php?us...eenv.3.exe[/url]
pogo 100% fixed and I added a menu, world map, enemies, a new level and sped it up a bit. Oh and there is sound and music now.
I used Ilsoap and Xkylyr Rauh music pack ( I hope thats allright, if not I will take it out.) I havent gotten around to credits for the game yet so I will just credit them here for now.
